Welcome to the Cartagen framework! If you're a developer looking to edit Cartagen source files, you're in the right place!

=================================================
Getting started

The first resource you should look at is the Cartagen Wiki Developer Center:

http://wiki.cartagen.org/wiki/show/DeveloperCenter

API Documentation for Cartagen are available at both http://cartagen.org/api/ and also in the Cartagen source at /public/api/index.html

=================================================
Cartagen source layout

http://wiki.cartagen.org/wiki/show/NavigatingTheSource

=================================================
Patches

To generate a code patch, look at this good outline for git patch submission: https://rails.lighthouseapp.com/projects/8994/sending-patches